# sorane content site

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root for full instructions.

## Quick rules

- Edit only `content/**/*.md` and `sorane.yaml`; never `dist/`
- Frontmatter: `type` (`article` | `index`), `title`, `profile: sorane-okf/0.1`
- After edits: `validate --cwd .` → `index --force` (if search) → `build --clean`
- sorane CLI: `node "$SORANE_ROOT/packages/cli/src/main.ts"` (see AGENTS.md)